snippet.title: Blooming Panic Trailer | Indie Visual Novel
snippet.description:
Depressed day-in and day-out from a draining corporate job, you become invested in a fantasy webnovel and find a mysterious link to a fan server. Everyone is warm and welcoming, but three members take a special interest in you! 

https://robobarbie.itch.io/blooming-panic
